text: Thorsten Johansson (9 October 1950 - 18 January 2021) was a Swedish sprinter. He competed in the men's 200 metres at the 1976 Summer Olympics. Johansson died on 18 January 2021, aged 70. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Swedish sprinters Category:Olympians for Sweden
